{"tid":1475722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港人真係好健忘！！！","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T03:32:13.000Z","uid":294072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3b57e2fe36d5ba120153e5955f8bfe80c8372af7","tid":1475722,"uid":294072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"「傳牛奶公司下令配合警方 主動交7-11萬寧CCTV以便捉人」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190813/59927204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190813%2F59927204&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=bb7fc47d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190813%2F59927204&h=bd8552cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190813/59927204</a><br />\n<br />\n難得牛\b奶公司咁保護我地市民，我地係咪應該幫襯啲先？<br />\n唔知仲有咩揀？唔\b緊要，我整左幅\b圖方便大家參考。出街揀餐廳就唔驚揀錯啦？<br />\n<br />\n其實牛奶公司旗下嘅美心係有好多\b餐廳，想\b知多啲，可以睇下\b下面邊條link啵<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/19mjGsUWwrZfvo22len5q0yzd_lYUW5JSymIzlfCo-HE/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F19mjGsUWwrZfvo22len5q0yzd_lYUW5JSymIzlfCo-HE%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=5a726404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/19mjGsUWwrZfvo22len5q0yzd_lYUW5JSymIzlfCo-HE/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n#曲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ci6D6gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fci6D6gd.jpg&h=b8af8746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBetween, 自由閪個app幾時出？"},{"pid":"1cb237d6caf0c760aa97ec7cb9558f60c54e3676","tid":1475722,"uid":294072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:41:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b7576d22b73c93a28957cb9458e7b9404120be6","tid":1